column1: # core data before year 2003 are not yet included
# name: the core name in PRIS
# power: the thermal design power in MW
# shutdown: YYYY-MM of permanent core shutdown (or way in the future)
# lat: core latitude in decimal degrees north
# lon: core longitude in decimal degrees east
# elevation: elevation above WGS84 reference ellipsoid in meters
# type: ie PWR BWR GCR PHWR LWGR FBR etc
# mox: 1 if using mixed oxide fuel or 0 if not
